    <item>
      <title>诺沃格拉茨称特朗普政府建立比特币战略储备的可能性很低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/novogratz-says-odds-are-low-that-trump-sets-up-bitcoin-strategic-reserve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币投资公司 Galaxy Digital 的亿万富翁负责人迈克尔·诺沃格拉茨表示，美国按照当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的提议建立比特币战略储备的可能性很小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/novogratz-says-odds-are-low-that-trump-sets-up-bitcoin-strategic-reserve</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 16:00:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>玫瑰碗将在特朗普就任前通过免税债券进行债务再融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/the-rose-bowl-moves-on-from-build-america-bonds-after-trump-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玫瑰碗体育场是位于洛杉矶东北部的一座拥有 102 年历史的体育场，其管理人员本周前往华尔街，将应税的“建设美国债券”返还为免税债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/the-rose-bowl-moves-on-from-build-america-bonds-after-trump-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 15:53:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Galaxy 的 Novogratz 表示比特币将达到 50 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-13/galaxy-s-novogratz-says-bitcoin-is-going-to-500k-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着当选总统唐纳德·特朗普获胜，比特币价格继续创下新高，首次突破 90,000 美元。Galaxy Digital 创始人兼首席执行官迈克·诺沃格拉茨表示，如果美国建立比特币储备，该代币的价格可能会飙升至 500,000 美元。他正在“彭博未平仓合约”上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-13/galaxy-s-novogratz-says-bitcoin-is-going-to-500k-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 15:50:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自由媒体的马菲卸任，二十年的交易宣告结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/liberty-media-s-maffei-steps-down-capping-two-decades-of-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自由媒体公司 (Liberty Media Corp.) 首席执行官格雷格·马菲 (Greg Maffei) 将于今年年底卸任，此前他已为董事长约翰·马龙 (John Malone) 的媒体、体育和电信帝国效力了近二十年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/liberty-media-s-maffei-steps-down-capping-two-decades-of-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 15:45:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>救援谈判陷入僵局，Northvolt 召开股东大会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/northvolt-calls-shareholder-meeting-as-rescue-talks-bog-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，电池制造商 Northvolt AB 于周三召开股东大会，筹集 3 亿美元紧急资金的谈判已进入关键时刻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/northvolt-calls-shareholder-meeting-as-rescue-talks-bog-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 15:37:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通胀数据公布后市场预期美联储 12 月降息概率达 80%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/traders-boost-bets-on-december-fed-cut-after-in-line-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在通胀数据符合预期后，交易员们加大了对美联储下个月将利率再次降息四分之一个百分点的押注，刺激美国国债上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/traders-boost-bets-on-december-fed-cut-after-in-line-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 13:55:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
